启动服务器 sudo /opt/sphinx/bin/searchd -c /opt/sphinx/etc/song.conf  
停止运行 sudo /opt/sphinx/bin/searchd -c /opt/sphinx/etc/song.conf --stop 
重新建立索引  sudo /opt/sphinx/bin/indexer -c /opt/sphinx/etc/song.conf --all 
cannot find MySQL include files 从源代码安装的环境 sudo aptitude install libmysql++-dev libmysqlclient15-dev checkinstall 
搜索数字id等  select  CONCAT(id)... 
